
#######################################################################################################
#                                        Passo a Passo
#######################################################################################################

1. Criar projeto mvn
  $ make

2. Em outro terminal copiar o arquivo.chat para a pasta sdi-dropbox que foi criada
  $ scp arquivo.chat aluno1@10.20.218.193:chatDropbox/sdi-dropbox

3. Em outro termianl abrir pasta criada
  $ cd sdi-dropbox

4. Compilar o servidor
  $ make server

5. Em outro terminal, abrir a pasta criada
  $cd sdi-dropbox

6. No mesmo terminal do item 5, compilar o cliente
  $ make client

  #######################################################################################################
  #                                        Observações
  #######################################################################################################

Há uma pasta com o nome do usuário, por exemplo: jose/ jose, dentro dela há o arquivo que será compartilhado.
O ChatServer baixa os arquivos que estão na pasta saida de cada cliente e faz o upload em server_dir.
A troca de mensagens acontece automaticamente, você só precisa adicionar um arquivo na pasta do usuário. Este arquivo será compartilhado com os demais.
